title: moved EUW to Oceania - help me cope with the pain that is levelling up (Supp main)
body:
I moved from EUW to Oceania due to now living in Oz, I'm a Supp main and looking for people to just play normals with me so I can just {{summoner:4}}  through it to get to ranked games. (currently lvl 7)

I placed S3 and ended B4 as I thought Soraka was a good idea when I hadn't read her skills properly. I started playing the game halfway through season 5, Keen to learn and develop my skills.

Hey who knows maybe I'll be good enough, or you'll teach me enough so that some of you guys would want to play ranked with me.

Oceania - Supportwisp
EUW (if you want reference) - this1game1sucks 
bearing in mind I literally made a league account to troll my friends in the EU at first but now I have a love for the game.

Add supportwisp and comment if you could help me out {{champion:201}}
